---
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script is:inline async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-DC032Y6PFZ"></script>
    <script is:inline>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());

      gtag('config', 'G-DC032Y6PFZ');
    </script>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <title>Terms & Conditions - 16-0 Play</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Terms and Conditions for 16-0play. Read the rules, guidelines, and terms of use for playing our cricket simulation game." />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-[var(--color-canvas-soft)] text-[var(--color-ink)] selection:bg-yellow-500/30">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-[var(--color-ink)]">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-[var(--color-body)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
        <p>Welcome to 16-0play!</p>
        <p>These terms and conditions outline the rules and regulations for the use of 16-0play's Website, located at 16-0play.com.</p>
        <p>By accessing this website we assume you accept these terms and conditions. Do not continue to use 16-0play if you do not agree to take all of the terms and conditions stated on this page.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] mt-8">License</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise stated, 16-0play and/or its licensors own the intellectual property rights for all material on 16-0play. All intellectual property rights are reserved. You may access this from 16-0play for your own personal use subjected to restrictions set in these terms and conditions.</p>
        
        <p>You must not:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Republish material from 16-0play</li>
          <li>Sell, rent or sub-license material from 16-0play</li>
          <li>Reproduce, duplicate or copy material from 16-0play</li>
          <li>Redistribute content from 16-0play</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] mt-8">Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, we exclude all representations, warranties and conditions relating to our website and the use of this website. Nothing in this disclaimer will:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>limit or exclude our or your liability for death or personal injury;</li>
          <li>limit or exclude our or your liability for fraud or fraudulent misrepresentation;</li>
          <li>limit any of our or your liabilities in any way that is not permitted under applicable law; or</li>
          <li>exclude any of our or your liabilities that may not be excluded under applicable law.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-[var(--color-ink)] hover:text-yellow-600 font-semibold transition-colors">
          &larr; Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
